      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i really dont think i can make an appointment this week, things are just too crazy with exams and my doctor is always booked out for weeks. if i just take it once in a while when i'm feeling really bad, like just a single pill, is that really gonna do anything? it's just a plant, surely my body can handle that better than a synthetic drug. it feels way safer than increasing my prescription.",
